Tidytext mining

#https://www.tidytextmining.com/tidytext.html
library(tidyverse)
library(tidytext)
library(wordcloud)
library(stringr)
report <- readRDS("data/report.rds")
text_df <- tibble(line = 1:19195, text = report$text_sep)

text_df <-text_df %>%
  unnest_tokens(word, text)

data(stop_words)
tidy_df <- text_df %>%
  anti_join(stop_words)

tidy_numbers <- text_df %>%
  filter(!is.na(as.numeric(word)))

tidy_df <- tidy_df %>%
  anti_join(tidy_numbers)
  
word_count <- tidy_df %>%
  count(word, sort = TRUE) 
word_count
## # A tibble: 10,779 x 2

#write_csv(word_count, "data/mueller_report_words.csv")

na.exclude(tidy_df) %>%
  count(word, sort = TRUE) %>%
  filter(n > 200) %>%
  mutate(word = reorder(word, n)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(word, n)) +
  geom_col() +
  xlab(NULL) +
  coord_flip() +
  theme(text = element_text(size=10))

wordcloud(word_count$word, word_count$n, max.words = 100, random.order = FALSE, scale = c(3, .7))
